Notwithstanding the permissions granted above, the following uses are
explicitly prohibited:

1. Training restriction. This Software, in whole or in part, may NOT be used
   as training data, fine-tuning data, or evaluation data for any artificial
   intelligence or machine learning model, system, or product.

2. Inference restriction. This Software, in whole or in part, may NOT be
   ingested, indexed, stored, or retrieved by any AI system for the purpose
